mairix: mairix - a program for indexing and searching email messages
mairix:
mairix: mairix is a program for indexing and searching email messages stored 
mairix: in Maildir, MH or mbox folders.
mairix: Some features:
mairix: * Indexing is fast. It runs incrementally on new messages 
mairix: * The search mode populates a "virtual" maildir (or MH) folder with 
mairix:   symlinks which point to the real messages. 
mairix: * The search mode is very fast.
mairix: * Indexing and searching works on the basis of words. 
mairix: mairix is licensed under the GPL.
